title: The Infowarrior - Featuring Jason Bermas-5-5-09.Commercial Free.
description:
The Info Warrior Show(internet radio) with Jason Bermas May 5th,2009 from prisonplanet.tv - Commercial free. 64Kbps.mp3


Alex Jones Takes the helm for the start of the show, once again, and goes on a short rant on several subjects, mostly media manipulation and internet free speech. Jason discusses Iran's role in recent bombings on Iraq and other recent news, plus takes calls.

Not my edit today, props to UKStewart82 for this one.
